  <brief_title>Efficacy and Safety Study of Panobinostat in Patients With Metastatic Hormone Refractory Prostate Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase II, Open Label, Single Arm Study of i.v. Panobinostat (LBH589) in Patients With Metastatic Hormone Refractory Prostate Cancer</official_title>
  <sponsors>
