  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This Phase II single dose study is designed to characterize the safety, tolerability and
      efficacy of i.v. panobinostat as a single-agent treatment in patients with hormone refractory
      prostate cancer.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
